snippet.title: New Rally X - Namco Arcade Game 1981 (1080p)
snippet.description:
New Rally-X is a maze and driving arcade game that was released by Namco in 1981. The player controls a blue car. The objective is to collect all the flags in the maze while avoid crashing into the rocks and the red cars controlled by the computer.

To play this game on PC click the link below:

http://www.retrouprising.com/arcade.php?act=Arcade&do=play&gameid=5894
